metadata.name: CryptoSkull Balloon #1/1000
metadata.description:
CryptoSkull Balloon is the CryptoSkulls version of Nyan Balloon, a personal and obligatory tribute to two masterpieces of pixel art and NFTs.

CryptoSkulls are 10,000 collectible ERC-721 Non-Fungible Tokens (NFTs). It's the 2nd 10k Profile Picture (PFP) collection on the Ethereum blockchain after CryptoPunks. Created by OG Alex Slayer.

Make sure to follow CryptoSkulls on Twitter: @Crypto_Skulls
